cs.AR, cs.GR, cs.DC, cs.ET, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the mapping of 2D and 3D geometrical transformations on a reconfigurable computing prototype for graphics acceleration. This falls under the categories of computer graphics (cs.GR) and embedded systems (cs.ET). The use of reconfigurable computing also brings in the category of computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper also discusses the performance improvements achieved, which falls under the category of performance evaluation (cs.PF) and system optimization (cs.SY).
